{"tid":85624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲左報力撐 林鄭：蘋果、東方、信報都對我嚴厲批評","createTime":"2017-01-18T12:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T14:59:56.000Z","uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a02e7c495fa02c3949e3ad30e10f246b3a9a658","tid":85624,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:55:27.000Z","msg":"已宣布參選的前政務司司長林鄭月娥今早出席電台節目。對於表態參選以來，獲親中報章《文匯報》、《大公報》等力撐，林鄭認為，這只是新聞自由，「<span style=\"color: red;\">從傳媒報道，同樣地、無可否認，《蘋果》、《東方》、《信報》自從12月10日之後，對我的批評，都相當嚴厲</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭認為，這只是香港的「傳媒生態」、「新聞自由」，「就算美國選舉，華盛頓郵報、紐約時報有哂立場，大家唔需要太過緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n主持人指《文匯報》、《大公報》不是一般傳媒，某程度反映中央路線，林鄭反稱，「其他傳媒你都知道，佢哋立場點樣。最終都係畀市民評論行政長官參選人。」<br />\n<br />\n對於主持人問到工聯會黃國健等部分建制派，已表態較支持她，林鄭稱，今次選舉四位參選人，當中三位都是政務官，長期擔任政府、議會工作，個別人士對參選人有既定看法，是正常不過，「<span style=\"color: red;\">有些人話我唔聽人意見，話我隻手遮天、話我愈來愈惡，都係每位人的言論自由。」</span><br />\n<br />\n有建制派透過中央處理兩司長辭職先後的問題，解讀中央更屬意林鄭參選，林鄭稱，各人有各人解讀，但她自己認為，「當知道第二位司長，有意辭職的時候參選，如果兩位司長都請辭，有兩個任命要做，係咪應該一併、全局睇先做呢？」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥提到，全國政協副主席董建華在她宣布要重新考慮是否參選後，有主動接觸，要求她認真考慮參選；競選辦主任陳智思亦透過短訊表示支持。林鄭月娥說，不方便代陳智思回應，他是否一早應承為曾俊華助選；至於她是否「撬」了曾俊華的班底，<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭則稱相信陳智思「咁大個人」，有其個人考量，會尊重決定。</span>"},{"pid":"5466615b75bb6b5e37816c7ba52a119fdd64f7bf","tid":85624,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"屹屹屹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自我感覺良好"},{"pid":"faccd94318ab0e847d06ba574a4bfcaa503c04be","tid":85624,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"唔屌成報既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夠膽屌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5bbaf866108b95b63adc603043e17af047c1dc","tid":85624,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"冇成報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08d7ec8bed0b543c5f73ba5b03cc4c120d762fb","tid":85624,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:48:25.000Z","msg":"諗多左，根本冇放過成報在眼內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db6f26c8c1917fd3582b542610da7d8ec1cdac5","tid":85624,"uid":42909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"唔敢屌成報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過搞清楚<br />\n成報先係代表中央立場<br />\n大公文匯係中聯辦立場"},{"pid":"e3f240c567ba2d06beb01ecbbebf2699da48d03a","tid":85624,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"無成報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9d2acec9c150ac2f51fe5214c69db4caf7f5ee","tid":85624,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"屈埋東方，明明東方都未站邊。"},{"pid":"31eb8624c84de9010b305651ff096a43b70faeb8","tid":85624,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無成報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同689一樣，唔夠膽提成報。"},{"pid":"4430b9347b8c635542c1e56f0a36cd8a90bcdb8c","tid":85624,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95a71578544714d06de34aed0d398e884d6e67eb","tid":85624,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"成報又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c384007a0d66a8d3f68ec1c79d4514a1b077d4e","tid":85624,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:15:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屈埋東方，明明東方都未站邊。</blockquote><br />\n之前東方頭條屌鳩過淋病故宮偷步</blockquote><br />\n//大家睇得一清二楚喇，有人未上台已經冇規冇矩打橫行，將來有機會坐正，實行隻手遮天，化身獨裁者都似。特首宣布放棄連任，好多人熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱，以為香港從此有運行，其實可能係前門拒狼，後門進虎嘅咋。（1月8日 東方）<br />\n兩大報都搞林鄭，仲加埋成報01，奶媽今次得個明報同tvb撐-.-"},{"pid":"297a4dfcb4c469061f1826f6619fed83fe8e2e76","tid":85624,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"咁係咪唔將成報放在眼內呀？"},{"pid":"4030fa0e4c89bfe0fb805996179f89e352ea43af","tid":85624,"uid":41500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"成報: 冇我份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公平咩"},{"pid":"f0f2f8b6e614e6eacab1332e60007e297943e63a","tid":85624,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"成報又羸一次,淋病唔敢鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都做成報頭版,可能當左成報係支持佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b7f67625bc4e7a17b4d9a35860d67ebc7da69a","tid":85624,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係咪唔將成報放在眼內呀？</blockquote><br />\n唔敢放入眼內，如果俾人問到，點回應。"},{"pid":"73ef5ebb01783a47562f67b548b52e19d890d56c","tid":85624,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"啲記者真係好撚渣...搵人問吓佢上帝把聲係點又唔問, 問佢點解唔提成報又唔問"},{"pid":"9beb5d5be1a4086dbd1d59d495664be592deaca2","tid":85624,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"關咩選特狗事<br />\n<br />\n講到黑箱作業本身無爭議咁<br />\n<br />\n就算早一年爆都係咁多人出聲屌架啦"},{"pid":"55dac60f207963d29cd40bfc26fde7440fcfb063","tid":85624,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無成報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同689一樣，唔夠膽提成報。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}